Steps to run the simulation:

1. Install anaconda following the appropriate steps for your OS
2. Add the conda-forge channel to your installation
	$ conda config --add channels conda-forge
	$ conda config --set channel_priority strict
3. Create a fresh Python 3.7 anaconda env called lunarGNSS and activate it
	$ conda create -n lunarGNSS -y python==3.7
	$ conda activate lunarGNSS
4. Install the necessary conda packages:
	$ conda install orekit pip numpy pandas plotly tqdm
5. Finally, install pymoo using pip
	$ pip install pymoo

Read the comments in main.py which will instruct you on how to operate the scripts
